      "content": "Cool, thanks. I mainly want to make sure they don't feel like they're losing the \"personal touch\" they're used to with you. Since the new model is optimized for speed, it might feel a bit more transactional or less nuanced in its travel recommendations. Can you write a guide that explains this change, but maybe highlights some of the complexities in high-end itinerary planning that a faster, more streamlined model might struggle to capture? I want them to be prepared for a shift in the level of detail they get.",
